%livy2.spark

val renameComplications_Deaths = nComplicationsDeaths.withColumnRenamed("Facility Name","Facility_Name").withColumnRenamed("Measure ID","Measure_ID").withColumnRenamed("Start Date","Start_Date").withColumnRenamed("End Date","End_Date")

val replaceQuotation = renameComplications_Deaths.withColumn("Facility_Name", regexp_replace($"Facility_Name","INC",""))
val replaceQuotation2 = replaceQuotation.withColumn("Facility_Name", regexp_replace($"Facility_Name","LLC",""))
val replaceQuotation3 = replaceQuotation2.withColumn("Facility_Name", regexp_replace($"Facility_Name","\"",""))

val replaceComplications_Deaths = replaceQuotation3.withColumn(
    "Facility_Name",
    when(
        $"Facility_Name".equalTo(" "),
        null
        ).otherwise($"Facility_Name")).withColumn(
    "Score",
    when(
        $"Score".equalTo("Not Available"),
        null
        ).otherwise($"Score")).withColumn(
    "Score",
    when(
